text: Augustine Tunde Oladapo (born 27 July 1995) is a Nigerian international footballer who plays for Enyimba, as a midfielder. ==Career== He has played club football for Ifeanyi Ubah, Kwara United, Gombe United and Enyimba. He made his international debut for Nigeria in 2018. ==References== Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Nigerian footballers Category:Nigeria international footballers Category:Ifeanyi Ubah F.C. players Category:Kwara United F.C. players Category:Gombe United F.C. players Category:Enyimba International F.C. players Category:Association football midfielders
